reviews.review_text:
Streaming song order is wrong if you stream this show disk three is played first followed by disks 1 and 2.  If you play with the embedded player the names are incorrect. The names in the player are in correct disk 1->2->3 order, but the files are not.

I have not yet listened to the show. Sound is good.
